# SPO-WebHooks .gitignore
# Based on the standard .NET .gitignore

## Build outputs
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]in/
out/
publish/

## NuGet packages
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/
packages/
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nuspec

## Visual Studio files
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs
*.DotSettings.user

## Rider
.idea/
*.sln.iml

## MSBuild
msbuild.log
msbuild.err
msbuild.wrn

## Test results
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage*/
TestResults/

## NuGet restore
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

## Build caches
.dotnet/
.tools/

## OS artifacts
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

## Certificates (never commit private keys or pfx files)
*.pfx
*.p12
*.key
*.pem
certs/

## Secrets / environment overrides
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
appsettings.Production.json
.env
.env.*
secrets.json
